                    Lead Document Controller &amp; Systems Developer with <strong>@((int)((DateTime.Now - new DateTime(2013, 6, 1)).TotalDays / 365.25))+ years</strong> of experience
                    in construction QA/QC, digital systems development, and process automation. I combine software engineering
                    expertise with deep field knowledge of <strong>welding, NDT, and QC workflows</strong> to deliver
                    efficient, scalable digital solutions.
                </p>
                <p class="about-text">
                    My flagship project — <strong>PMS (Piping Management System)</strong> — is an enterprise
                    <strong>ASP.NET Core 8</strong> platform deployed on <strong>Riyas NGL &amp; Jafurah Gas Processing Projects</strong>,
                    supporting <strong>20+ daily users</strong> and <strong>120,000+ welded joints</strong> — handling
                    DFR/DWR reports, joint tracking, NDE/RT selection, welder qualifications,
                    automated PDF generation, and Azure OCR document digitisation.
                </p>

